{
  "stem": "15393.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Indeed, within a year-- I'll be now brief, because-- within a year of my arrival-- not exactly a year, a year and two months of my arrival-- we managed to bring my mother over.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Schoenberg was extremely helpful in that my school helped me, many people helped me, but they actually brought her over as a domestic to this country.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she arrived here in May '47.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She had five pounds in her pocket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was not allowed to go and meet her at the station, because it was Sabbath, and they wouldn't let me go.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was absolutely terrible, because she came to a totally strange foreign country without a word of English, nothing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Here am I, and I'm not waiting for her at the station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They wouldn't allow me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They locked me in, they wouldn't let me go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she was waiting and waiting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You can imagine how I feel-- or how I felt, rather.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was waiting for quite some time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as I wasn't coming, she didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She thought maybe I had an accident, god knows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the five pounds, which she was allowed to take out of Poland and bring into here, she hired a taxi.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She brought a sewing machine and five pounds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She hired a taxi, which cost her 3 pounds 50, and she was left with 1 pound 50 in her pocket when she arrived here and came to my school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was all right, for her to come by taxi, on a Sabbath, to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But for me to go and fetch her was not all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You can see the hypocrisy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Anyway, so I rebelled a lot about this type of hypocrisy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
